bubba-backend (1.1.142) estelle; urgency=low

  * Relativelty large rewrite of backup backend to produce more and better
    error messages.
    Includes adding json output to parts of restore-process.
    Added a function to use for ssh "test connection" (currently only used to
    solve ssh errors during restore operations).

